   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Col. I);;Year 33 of Lucius Aelius Aurelius Commodus Caesar the lord, Mecheir 6 for the account of Mecheir. Ptolemaios, son of Mysthes the son of Ptolemaios, and of Tak(--), has paid for the poll tax of the 32nd year in the district of Hiera Pyle twenty drachmai, that is 20 dr., with additional payments of 10 obols.;;(Col. II);;Year 33 of Lucius Aelius Aurelius Commodus Caesar the lord, Mecheir 6 for the account of Mecheir. Ision, son of Ptolemaios the son of heron, and of Tap(--), has paid for the poll tax of the 32nd year in the district of Hiera Pyle twenty drachmai, that is 20 dr., with additional payments of 10 obols.</ab>
         </div>
